    en: { name: "MUZA Park (Bustan)", role: "Public park", zone: "Western park",
         desc: "The Jack, Joseph & Morton Mandel public park in the western grounds — free to enter, with a pond, an orchard and shaded “sheep-track” paths lined with seating, fountains, grapevine trellises and native Mediterranean planting. Within it: the Park Pond, the Olive Press and Flour Mill, the Planetarium, Sundial Square and the Folklore Pavilion.",
